ypr.Rd

Yield-Per-Recruit

ypr(tmax = 20L, k = 0.1, Linf = 100, t0 = 0, a = 1e-05, b = 3,
  Llo = Linf/2, Lup = Linf, mu = 0.2, Lm = Linf/2, fa = a, fb = b)

Arguments

tmax

The maximum age.
k

The growth coefficient.
Linf

The mean maximum length.
t0

The age at length 0.
a

The condition factor.
b

The scaling exponent.
Llo

The lower harvest length.
Lup

The upper harvest length.
mu

The annual interval mortality rate.
Lm

The length at maturity.
fa

The fecundity factor.
fb

The fecundity scaling exponent.
